Package com.company

Class Architecture

java.lang.Object
com.company.Architecture
All Implemented Interfaces:
Focused, Heighted, Lengthed, Positioned
Direct Known Subclasses:
Building, Playground
public abstract class Architecture extends Object implements Positioned, Lengthed, Heighted, Focused
Architecture is the abstract base class for all things that can be constructed on a street and has properties of position, length, and height and has a functionality of being focused on.
